The non-vanishing components of the energy-momentum tensor using (\ref{E-M}) are
\begin{eqnarray}
T^t_t &=& -\frac{1}{2} \Omega ^2(\phi) \left\{ -g^{tt} \sigma ^2 {P_t}^2 + g^{rr} \left[{\varphi ^\prime}^2 +{\sigma ^\prime}^2\right]+ g^{\theta \theta}
\varphi ^2Q^2 \right\} \nonumber \\
&-& \frac{1}{8\pi}  g^{rr} \left\{-g^{tt}
